sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    title Chat Request Lifecycle

    actor Student
    participant Web as Web App
    participant API as Cloud Functions
    participant DB as Firestore
    participant LLM as OpenAI

    Student->>Web: Ask question
    Web->>DB: Save user message
    Web->>API: POST /chat
    API->>DB: Load chat and material context
    API->>LLM: Generate answer
    loop Stream answer
        LLM-->>API: Text chunk
        API-->>Web: SSE chunk
    end
    API->>DB: Save session state
    Web->>DB: Save AI answer + citations
    Web-->>Student: Show answer
